TAX REFUND SZN IS APPROACHING!!

Everyone knows that refunds will begin at the beginning of next year. If you guys are getting a refund, how are you going to use that discretionary money that you have the most beneficial way possible. Yes, use that money and have some fun. Life is all about making experiences for yourself, but also create some longevity. Let’s put that money somewhere where it can grow and not only grow but used tax efficiently. Also, if you guys are business owners or in a higher tax bracket than most people and want to figure out some ways to better utilize your money and more strategically plan for taxes let me know. Let’s be smart in 2024 when it comes to finances. ✨💰

#financialfreedom #taxes #financialadvisor #explore #fyp

Those who are disciplined with money, are disciplined every aspect of their life. I don’t wake up at 4:30 every morning because I have to I do it because I get the opportunity to be better than I was the day before. There’s something about someone who could wake up consistently before anyone else and go do something that makes them uncomfortable because they know in the long run it’ll pay dividends. I hope this shows those who work with me that not only do I care about their wealth, but I always preach health is also wealth. Get up and get the money! I am THE ATL FINANCE GUY!💰
 
#financialfreedom #finance #workout #work

YOU VS YOU. 
If you had a conversation with yourself in five years, would you be happy about the decisions you’re making right now? would you have wanted to do more? So often I hear “man you’re starting so young I wish I would’ve did that when I was your age” so I just do it. I’m saving right now. I’m investing right now. I’m taking care of my body right now, I’m not procrastinating anything I see what I want to do in life and I know it starts now. Are you doing what it takes to be the best version of yourself in five years or next year if it’s financially mentally, spiritually, physically…. just start NOW. 

ATL FINANCE GUY!💰
